1) Timber Drive Elementary & Vandora Springs Elementary are
located less than 1 mile from the studied intersection but were
not in session on the date of the count, as all Wake County
Schools were on Spring Break. MEI proceeded with count
because NCDOT instructed count to be taken on April 4, 2012.
2) As requested, U-turns were counted instead of pedestrians.
4) Area lighting was present at the count location.
5) No highway construction was observed that impacted normal

8) The counter did not have any additional notes.
